{
  "chapter": "003",
  "title": "殷本纪",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "契之降生",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">殷契</span>，母亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简狄</span>，是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有娀氏</span>的女儿，做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝喾</span>的次妃。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>一起去洗澡，看见<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">玄鸟</span>掉下一枚卵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简狄</span>取来吞下去，因而怀孕，生了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>长大以后辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>治水有功。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">命</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不亲睦，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五品</span>不顺从，你担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司徒</span>，恭敬地推行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五教</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五教</span>的推行要宽厚。\" 封<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">商</span>地，赐姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">子氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>兴起于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">大禹</span>之间，功业显著于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>因此得以安定。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "先公世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭明</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昭明</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">相土</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">相土</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌若</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌若</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹圉</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹圉</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冥</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冥</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">振</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">振</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">微</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">微</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">报丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">报丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">报乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">报乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">报丙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">报丙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主壬</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主壬</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主癸</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">主癸</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">天乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "成汤居亳",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>的时代，从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，共迁都八次。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>开始时居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>，沿袭<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的居地，作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">帝诰</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "汤伐葛伯",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>征讨<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">葛伯</span>不祭祀，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>首先<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>他。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>说：\"我有一句话：人看水能照见自己的形貌，看民众就能知道治理得好不好。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>说：\"说得明白啊！能够听从忠言，治道才能进步。治理国家爱护百姓，做善事的人都能入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">王官</span>任职。勉励啊，勉励啊！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>说：\"你们若不能恭敬奉命，我就要大加惩罚<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">殛</span>杀，没有可以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>的。\""
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "作汤征",
      "text": "作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">汤征</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "伊尹归汤",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阿衡</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阿衡</span>想进见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>而没有门路，就做了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有莘氏</span>陪嫁的臣仆，背着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎俎</span>，用烹调滋味来游说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>施行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>。也有人说，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>本是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">处士</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>派人去聘请迎接他，往返了五次，然后才肯前来跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，讲论素王及九主的治国之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>举用他，委以国政。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>离开<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>去。已厌恶<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>的所为，又回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>。从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北门</span>进城，遇见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">女鸠</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">女房</span>，作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">女鸠女房</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "网开三面",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>出行，看见野外张着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">网</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四面</span>，祝祷说：\"从<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>四方来的都进入我的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">网</span>中。\""
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "去其三面",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>说：\"嘻，这是把它们赶尽杀绝啊！\" 于是去掉其中<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三面</span>，祝祷说：\"想向左的，就向左。想向右的，就向右。不听从天命的，才进入我的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">网</span>中。\""
    },
    "6.2": {
      "title": "伐昆吾讨桀",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>听说了，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>的德行到了极点啊，恩及<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">禽兽</span>。\" 当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏桀</span>施行暴政，荒淫无度，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">昆吾氏</span>作乱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>于是起兵率领<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>跟随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>亲自手持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钺</span>去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">昆吾</span>，接着<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>。"
    },
    "6.2.1": {
      "title": "汤誓",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>说：\"来，你们众人，都听我说。并不是我小子敢于兴兵作乱，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>多有罪恶，我听到了你们众人的怨言，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">夏氏</span>有罪。我畏惧<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">上帝</span>，不敢不前去征讨。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>多有罪恶，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">殛</span>灭它。如今你们众人说：'我们的君王不体恤我们众人，丢下我们的农事却去割据掠夺。'你们或许会说：'他有罪，又能把他怎样？'夏王制止众人的劳力，掠夺夏国。众人怠惰不合作，说：'这个太阳什么时候灭亡？我和你们宁可一起灭亡。'夏的德行到了这个地步，现在我必须前去。你们辅助我一人，施行上天的惩罚，我要重重赏赐你们。你们不要不相信，我决不食言。你们如果不遵从誓言，我就要把你们连同妻儿<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">僇</span>杀，没有可以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>的。\""
    },
    "6.3": {
      "title": "作汤誓",
      "text": "把誓词布告军众，作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">汤誓</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>说\"我很英武\"，号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：商武王\">武王（商武王）</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "汤胜夏桀",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">有娀之虚</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>逃奔到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸣条</span>，夏师全军覆没。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>接着<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三飐</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">俘获</span>其<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝玉</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义伯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲伯</span>作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">典宝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>已经<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">战胜</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>，想迁走夏的社坛，但没能办到，于是作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">夏社</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>禀告。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>全都归服，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>于是登上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之位，平定了海内。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "汤归作诰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>回来到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰卷陶</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中纻</span>作诰文。已罢<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">绌</span>夏的政令，回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">汤诰</span>。"
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "诰东郊",
      "text": "\"<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三月</span>，王亲自来到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东郊</span>。告谕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群后</span>：'都要对民众有功绩，努力做好你们的职事。否则我就要大加<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">殛</span>杀惩罚你们，不要怨我。'"
    },
    "8.2": {
      "title": "述先王功",
      "text": "又说：'从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>长期在外辛劳，对民众有功绩，民众因此得以安宁。东面疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>，北面疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>，西面疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，南面疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">四渎</span>已经治理，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">万民</span>才有了安居之地。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>教民播种，农民种植<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">百穀</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">三公</span>都对民众有功，所以他们的后代得以立国。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蚩尤</span>和他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">作乱</span>于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，上帝就不佑助他，有此明证。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的教诲不可以不勉力遵从。'"
    },
    "8.3": {
      "title": "戒不道者",
      "text": "又说：'不行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">正道</span>的人，不得立国，你们不要怨我。'\""
    },
    "8.4": {
      "title": "伊尹作咸有一德",
      "text": "把这些训令告谕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">咸有一德</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">咎单</span>作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">明居</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "改正朔易服色",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>于是修改<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">正朔</span>，变易<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">服色</span>，崇尚白色，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝会</span>定在白天举行。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "太甲继位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太丁</span>没有即位就死了，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太丁</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">外丙</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝外丙</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝外丙</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">外丙</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中壬</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中壬</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中壬</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">四年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太丁</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太甲</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太甲</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>的嫡长孙，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">伊训</span>，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">肆命</span>，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">徂后</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "伊尹放太甲",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span>即位已<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，昏庸不明，暴虐无道，不遵从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>的法度，败坏德行，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>把他放逐到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桐宫</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>摄政当国，接受<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的朝见。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "太甲悔过",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桐宫</span>居住<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，悔过自责，回归善道，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>就迎回<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span>，把政权交还给他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span>修养德行，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都归附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>因此得以安宁。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>赞许他，就作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">太甲训</span>三篇，赞扬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太甲</span>，称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：商太宗\">太宗（商太宗）</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "沃丁立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：商太宗\">太宗（商太宗）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沃丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝沃丁</span>的时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>。已将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">咎单</span>便陈述<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>的事迹，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">沃丁</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "殷道衰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沃丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太庚</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍己</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝雍己</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的国运衰落，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>有的不再来朝。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "太戊中兴",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝雍己</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太戊</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太戊</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太戊</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>为相。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>出现了怪异的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑</span>树和<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">穀</span>树一起长在朝堂上，一夜之间长到双手合抱那么粗。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太戊</span>害怕，问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>。"
    },
    "15.1": {
      "title": "伊陟进谏",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>说：\"臣听说<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">妖不胜德</span>，莫非帝的政事有什么过失吗？帝应当修养德行。\""
    },
    "15.2": {
      "title": "伊陟赞巫咸",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太戊</span>听从了，怪异的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑</span>树就枯死而消失了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>把这事告诉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">巫咸</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">巫咸</span>治理王家有功，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">咸艾</span>，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">太戊</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太戊</span>在庙中赞扬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>，表示不以臣礼相待，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊陟</span>谦让，作<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">原命</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>再度复兴，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>归附，所以称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中宗</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "中丁至河亶甲",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中宗</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中丁</span>迁都到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">隞</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">河亶甲</span>居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">相</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖乙</span>迁都到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邢</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">外壬</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝外壬</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲丁</span>的史书缺失不全。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝外壬</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">河亶甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝河亶甲</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">河亶甲</span>的时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>再度衰落。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "祖乙复兴",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">河亶甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖乙</span>即位，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>再度复兴。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">巫贤</span>任职为相。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "祖辛至阳甲",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖辛</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖辛</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沃甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝沃甲</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝沃甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沃甲</span>的哥哥<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖辛</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖丁</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖丁</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，立弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">沃甲</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">南庚</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝南庚</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝南庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖丁</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阳甲</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝阳甲</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝阳甲</span>的时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>衰落。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "九世之乱",
      "text": "自<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中丁</span>以来，废黜嫡子而改立诸弟子，弟子之间有时争相取代，接连<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九世</span>内乱，于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>不再来朝见。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "盘庚迁都",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝阳甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盘庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝盘庚</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝盘庚</span>的时候，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>已经建都于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河北</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盘庚</span>渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>向南，重新居住在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>的旧都，共迁都五次，没有固定的居所。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的民众都怨声载道，不愿迁徙。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盘庚</span>便告谕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>说：\"从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高后</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>和你们的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先祖</span>共同平定<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，所立的法度是可以遵行的。舍弃而不勉力去做，怎能成就德政！\" 于是便渡过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>向南，治理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>都，推行<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>的政令，然后<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>才得以安宁，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的国运再度复兴。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>前来朝见，因为他遵循了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>的德政。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "小辛小乙",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝盘庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">小辛</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小辛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小辛</span>即位，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>再度衰落。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>思念<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盘庚</span>，于是作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">盘庚</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三篇</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小辛</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">小乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小乙</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "武丁得说",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝小乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝武丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝武丁</span>即位后，想要复兴<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>，但没有得到辅佐之人。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>不发言，政事由<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">冢宰</span>决定，而自己察看<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">国风</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>夜里梦见得到<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span>，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅说\">说（傅说）</span>。把梦中所见之人的形貌比对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百吏</span>，都不是。于是派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百工</span>到野外去<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">营求</span>寻访，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">傅险</span>中找到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅说\">说（傅说）</span>。那时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：傅说\">说（傅说）</span>做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">胥靡</span>，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">傅险</span>筑墙。进见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>说就是这个人。得到后与他交谈，果然是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span>，举用他为相，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>国大治。于是就用<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">傅险</span>赐姓给他，号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">傅说</span>。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "祥雉之戒",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝武丁</span>祭祀<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">第二天</span>，有一只飞翔的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">雉</span>停在鼎耳上鸣叫，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>感到害怕。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖己</span>说：\"王不必忧虑，先要修好政事。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖己</span>于是劝导王说：\"上天监察下民，以义为准则，赐予的寿命有长有短，并非上天让人夭折，是人自己中途断绝了寿命。民众有不顺从德行的，不服从罪罚的，上天已经降命来纠正他们的德行，却还说'能把我怎样'。呜呼！王要继承先王恭敬对待民众的传统，没有不是承继天命的，祭祀要合常礼，不要用<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">弃道</span>的礼数。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>修明政事推行德政，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都欢悦，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的国运再度复兴。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "祖庚立高宗庙",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝武丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖己</span>赞赏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武丁</span>能以祥雉之事修德，立起他的庙号为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：帝武丁\">高宗（帝武丁）</span>，于是作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">高宗肜日</span>及<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">训</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "帝甲淫乱",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝祖庚</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝甲</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝甲</span>淫乱，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>再度衰落。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "武乙射天",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝廪辛</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝廪辛</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庚丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝庚丁</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝庚丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝武乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>再次离开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>，迁徙到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河北</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "武乙震死",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝武乙</span>无道，制作偶人，称它为天神。和它赌博，让人代行。天神不能取胜，就羞辱它。又做了一个革囊，装满血，仰头<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span>它，称为\"射天\"。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武乙</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河渭</span>之间打猎，遇到暴雷，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武乙</span>被震死。儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太丁</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝乙</span>即位后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>更加衰落。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "帝辛继位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝乙</span>的长子叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">微子启</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>的母亲地位低贱，不能继承王位。小儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：帝辛\">辛（帝辛）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：帝辛\">辛（帝辛）</span>的母亲是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">正后</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：帝辛\">辛（帝辛）</span>得以继承王位。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝乙</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：帝辛\">辛（帝辛）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">继位</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝辛</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>称他为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "纣王骄奢",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝纣</span>天资聪颖敏捷，见闻广博；气力过人，能徒手<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">格</span>斗<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">猛兽</span>；<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">知足以距谏，言足以饰非</span>；在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>面前夸耀自己的才能，向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>炫耀自己的声望，认为所有人都不如自己。 - 喜好喝酒纵情淫乐，迷恋<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>。宠爱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妲己</span>，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妲己</span>的话言听计从。 - 于是让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">师涓</span>创作新的靡靡之音，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北里</span>的舞蹈，颓靡的乐曲。 - 加重<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">赋税</span>来充实<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鹿台</span>的钱财，堆满<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜桥</span>的粮仓。 - 大肆搜集<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">奇物</span>，充塞<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宫室</span>。 - 大规模扩建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沙丘</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">苑台</span>，多方捕捉<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">野兽</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">蜚鸟</span>放在里面。 - 怠慢<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">鬼神</span>。 - 在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沙丘</span>大兴乐戏，以酒作池，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法·规范：悬挂\">县（悬挂）</span>肉成林，让男女裸体在其间相互追逐，通宵达旦地<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">长夜之饮</span>。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "三公之祸",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>怨恨，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>有人背叛，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>加重<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刑辟</span>，制定了<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">砲格之法</span>。任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">西伯昌</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂侯</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">三公</span>。 - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>有个美丽的女儿，进献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>的女儿不喜欢淫荡之事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>发怒，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了她，又把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>[剁成肉酱|醢。 - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂侯</span>极力争辩，言辞激烈，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>又把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鄂侯</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法·规范：脯\">制成肉脯（脯）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">西伯昌</span>听说后，暗自叹息。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">崇侯虎</span>知道了，报告给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚禁</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羑里</span>。 - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>的臣子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">闳夭</span>等人，寻找美女、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">奇物</span>、良<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">赦免</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>出来后献上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛西</span>之地，请求废除<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">砲格之刑</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>答应了，○赐给他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">弓矢</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">斧钺</span>，使他能够<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">征伐</span>别人，成为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>。 - 又任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">费中</span>执政。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">费中</span>善于阿谀，贪图利益，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>人都不亲近他。 - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>又任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">恶来</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">恶来</span>善于毁谤谗言，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>因此更加疏远。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "祖伊告纣",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>回国后，就暗中修养<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德行</span>多行善事，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>大多<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">背叛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>前来归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>势力日益壮大，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的权势因此逐渐失去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王子比干</span>进谏，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>不听。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商容</span>是位<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贤者</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>爱戴他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>却<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">罢黜</span>了他。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">饥国</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了它，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的臣子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖伊</span>听到后责怪<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>，又感到恐惧，跑去报告<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>说：\"上天已经断绝了我<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的天命，借助于人和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">元龟</span>占卜，没有敢预知吉兆的，并非<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>不佑助我<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">後人</span>，而是王淫乱暴虐自绝于天，所以上天<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">抛弃</span>了我们，使我们不得安食，不能察知天性，不遵循法典。如今我们的民众无不希望国家灭亡，说'上天为何不降威罚，大命为何还不到来'？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">今王</span>您要怎么办呢？\" - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>说：\"我生下来不是有天命在身吗！\" - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">祖伊</span>回去，说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>已经不可劝谏了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>去世后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>向东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>，到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">盟津</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">背叛</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>前来会合<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百</span>国。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>可以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周武王\">武王（周武王）</span>说：\"你们还不了解<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天命</span>。\" 于是又返回了。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "牧野之战",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>越发淫乱不止。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">微子</span>多次进谏不听，就和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大师</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">少师</span>商议，于是离开了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>说：\"做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>的，不能不以死相争。\" 就极力劝谏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>发怒说：\"我听说<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">圣人</span>的心有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七窍</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">剖</span>开<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>的胸膛，观看他的心。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>害怕，就假装发狂做奴仆，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>又囚禁了他。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大师</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">少师</span>便抱着祭祀的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乐器</span>投奔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>于是率领<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>也发兵在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牧野</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法·规范：抵抗\">距（抵抗）</span>。 - <span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">甲子日</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的军队<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战败</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>逃入城中，登上<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鹿台</span>，穿上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宝玉衣</span>，投火自焚而死。 - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的头，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法·规范：悬挂\">县（悬挂）</span>在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">白旗</span>上。<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">妲己</span>。 - <span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法·规范：释放\">释（释放）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">箕子</span>出囚禁，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">比干</span>的坟墓，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法·规范：表彰\">表（表彰）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商容</span>的乡里。 - <span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武庚</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禄父</span>，使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的祭祀得以延续，令他推行<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">盘庚</span>的政令。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的民众非常高兴。 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span>成为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。其后世贬降帝号，称为王。而封<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的后裔为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，隶属于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>。"
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "周公诛武庚",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周武王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">去世</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武庚</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管叔</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">蔡叔</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">作乱</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">命</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>◉诛灭他们，而○立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">微子</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宋</span>，以延续<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的后嗣。"
    },
    "34": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：我根据《颂》排列<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>的事迹，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成汤</span>以来，采自《尚书》和《诗经》。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>为<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">子姓</span>，他的后代<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">分封</span>，以国号为姓，于是有<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">殷氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">来氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">宋氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">空桐氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">稚氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">北殷氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">目夷氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>说，殷的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">路车</span>最美，而颜色崇尚白色。"
    },
    "35": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">简狄</span>吞卵，因此成为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的始祖。 玄王开创商业，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>背着俎器来归。 上面网开三面，下面献上九主之说。 班师回<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰卷</span>，继而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">臣扈</span>辅佐。 迁都于嚣又毁于耿，国土没有固定。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武乙</span>无道，祸端起于射天。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝辛</span>淫乱，拒绝忠谏残害贤良。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">九侯</span>被剁成肉酱，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">砲格</span>之刑兴起。 <span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄钺</span>被持来征伐，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">白旗</span>被高悬。 可叹那琼室华丽，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>的宗祀因此迁移！"
    }
  }
}